title: Miss Kuroitsu From the Monster Development Department
subTitle: In Japan, evil organizations battle superheroes for world domination. Miss Kuroitsu works for one such group, creating monsters to defeat a hero, while facing typical corporate challenges.

subTitle: When their involvement with the wrong people puts her and her family at risk, Ashley turns to her estranged father for help, who is living a retired life in the Cayman Islands.
